      "review_summary": "The PR updates the LM Studio embedding provider to resolve existing model/provider contextTokens and contextWindow config and pass the resolved value to ensureLmstudioModelLoaded, with regression tests for precedence cases.\n\nPR surface: Source +24, Tests +179. Total +203 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Source-level reproduction is high confidence: current main and v2026.6.10 call the LM Studio embedding load helper without requestedContextLength, while the helper defaults upward before sending context_length; I did not run a live CUDA repro.",
